text:
There are several programs for migrating to Australia.
They include:

(1) skilled migration scheme for people with skills and talents at various trades;

(2) family reunion for people with family in Australia;

(3) special eligibility for people who were former citizens or residents;

(4) humanitarian program for refugees and others in special need.

I enclose a link to the Australian Department of Immigration and Multicultural Affairs containing further information.

